label: Hādhihi al-Nubdhah al-mufīd al-mushtamilah ʻalá jawāhir masāʼil riyāḍat al-mubtadī wa-al-tamrīn wa-maʻrifat qawāʻid al-naḥw wa-ḥaqāʼiqihi nafaʻa Allāh taʻālá bi-hā al-ṭālib al-muhtadī.
